{
  "name": "mineradio",
  "productName": "Mineradio",
  "version": "1.1.2",
  "description": "沉浸式音乐播放器，融合天气电台、歌词舞台、粒子视觉和 3D 歌单架。",
  "author": "Mineradio",
  "main": "desktop/main.js",
  "private": true,
  "scripts": {
    "start": "electron .",
    "build:mac": "electron-builder --mac --publish never",
    "release:mac": "electron-builder --mac --publish always"
  },
  "releaseInfo": {
    "releaseNotes": "## Mineradio v1.1.2\n\n### 新功能\n- **弹幕评论系统**：支持弹幕滚动和卡片轮播两种模式\n- **卡片模式**：展示评论者头像、昵称、评论内容、时间、属地、点赞数\n- **滚动模式**：评论从右向左匀速滚动，支持字体大小、速度、密度调节\n- **玻璃效果**：弹幕和卡片采用毛玻璃背景，与播放器控制台风格统一\n\n### 优化改进\n- 评论数据上限提升至300条，洗牌算法确保不重复\n- 弹幕消失逻辑优化，所有弹幕从右到左全程滚动\n- 暂停/恢复后卡片状态正确恢复\n\n### Bug修复\n- 修复首次播放弹幕卡片不触发问题\n- 修复头像不显示问题\n- 修复滚动弹幕轨道槽位重叠问题\n\n### 其他\n- 新增联系作者按钮\n- 预设效果名称自动从配置文件读取"
  },
  "build": {
    "appId": "com.mineradio.desktop",
    "productName": "Mineradio",
    "directories": {
      "output": "dist",
      "buildResources": "build"
    },
    "afterPack": "build/after-pack.js",
    "files": [
      "desktop/**/*",
      "public/**/*",
      "build/**/*",
      "server.js",
      "dj-analyzer.js",
      "package.json",
      "public/index.html",
      "public/index.apple-test.html"
    ],
    "asar": false,
    "mac": {
      "icon": "build/icon.icns",
      "hardenedRuntime": false,
      "gatekeeperAssess": false,
      "target": [
        {
          "target": "dmg",
          "arch": [
            "x64",
            "arm64"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    "publish": [
      {
        "provider": "github",
        "owner": "ShijingYangwow27",
        "repo": "Mineradio--macOS"
      }
    ]
  },
  "mineradio": {
    "update": {
      "provider": "github",
      "owner": "ShijingYangwow27",
      "repo": "Mineradio--macOS",
      "preview": false,
      "preferMirrors": true,
      "mirrors": [
        "https://gh.llkk.cc/",
        "https://ghfast.top/",
        "https://gh-proxy.com/"
      ]
    }
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "gsap": "^3.15.0",
    "mpg123-decoder": "^1.0.3",
    "NeteaseCloudMusicApi": "^4.32.0",
    "pinyin-pro": "^3.28.1"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "electron": "^42.4.1",
    "electron-builder": "^26.15.3",
    "rcedit": "^5.0.2"
  },
  "optionalDependencies": {
    "koffi": "^3.0.2"
  }
}
